msg: As suggested by Andrew on dev ML, I put this Aptana formatting template in root repo.

It's also available as an attachment of OFBiz Contributors Best Practices page in wiki. It needs Eclipse/Aptana for editing Javascript files and notably to format them correctly. I suggest also to not use tabs in *our* javascript files but 4 spaces (like in Java)
